Despite being confident I’ve always been conscious and anxious about shooting videos in public. It’s something I’ve always wanted to do and I admire every creator who does it with so much ease 😭

However, in 2025 I’m going to challenge myself to shoot in public whenever I get the chance. These videos aren’t aimed to talk about products/show you how something is to be done but they’re meant for me to get out of my comfort zone🤓

Day 1 was a success ✅ even though I kept checking to see if someone was judging me 😭 

#contentcreation #challenge #2025challenge #selfimprovement #overcomingfear
